00:12:18,511 --> 00:12:21,534
The Things They Carried by Tim O'Brien,

229
00:12:21,534 --> 00:12:24,396
which is an amazing book.

230
00:12:24,396 --> 00:12:26,237
And then again, touching on the criminality

